      <tr> 
       <td width="15" height="1"> &nbsp;</td> 
       <td width="489" height="1" align="justify" colspan="3"> <span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial">Since 1998 this conference has been organized by public and private universities every year. More than four hundred papers have been submitted to this conference from Bangladesh, Australia, Canada, China, Germany, India, Iran, Japan, South Korea, Malaysia, New Zealand, Norway, Pakistan, Saudi Arabia, UK and USA. Of these, 136 papers and 20 poster presentations have been accepted. ICCIT 2010, co-sponsored by IEEE Bangladesh Section, is the largest technical event on computer Science and Engineering, Information and Communication in Bangladesh. Three day-long International Conference concluded on 25 December 2010. In the closing ceremony Prof. Dr. M. Anwar Hossain was the Chairman&nbsp; of the session. In the last day it was announced that the next ICCIT-2011 will be held in American International University from 22-24 December, 2011. In the end of the closing ceremony of ICCIT 2010 a colorful cultural program was organized also.</span></td> 
